revision.text: ==Translingual== ===Etymology=== Named in a pseudo-Latin manner for any of several naturalists named [[Yarrell]], but especially for naturalist [[w:William Yarrell|William Yarrell]]. ===Noun=== {{head|mul|noun form|genitive}} # [[Yarrell]] (attributive); used in taxonomic names for organisms that often have English names of the form "Yarrell's ..." ====Derived terms==== * {{taxlink|Bagarius yarrelli|species|noshow=1}} [[Category:Translingual taxonomic eponyms]]
